(112, 1, '2018-09-24 20:27:17', '2018-09-24 17:27:17', '<h1>Drum Facts - Information,Types, Components and Configuration</h1>\r\n<div class=\"addthis_inline_share_toolbox\"></div>\r\nOver the last several thousand years of our history, drums managed to integrate themselves into our culture, customs, and religious ceremonies. If you want to learn more about all the most interesting facts about drums, you have come to the right place.\r\n\r\nDrums are today integral part of our modern history and countless musical genres where rhythm section is powered by talented drummers that have customized their personal drum-kits. Here you can find out many interesting facts about oldest musical instrument in the world – drums.', 'Drums', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'drums', '', '', '2018-09-24 20:27:17', '2018-09-24 17:27:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=112', 0, 'page', '', 0),
