(151, 1, '2018-09-24 21:31:22', '2018-09-24 18:31:22', '<span class=\"a-size-base\">Bought this for our 10 year old son for his birthday and 5 months later he has not lessened in his excitement. He plays this set every single day. While it doesn\'t have quite the sound of an \"adult\" drum set, it does not sound like a toy set either. Set up wasn\'t too bad with the help of the dvd and now he likes to move around and tweak his set to his own liking. I wholeheartedly recommend as I searched long and hard for just the right set. He will eventually upgrade the cymbals as he has already started looking on amazon for new ones, but for now those are ok too</span>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.amazon.com/Gammon-Percussion-Complete-Cymbals-Stands/dp/B002RGPQJ0/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1537813733&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=drum+kit', 'drum kit', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '124-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-24 21:31:22', '2018-09-24 18:31:22', '', 124, 'http://localhost/wordpress/uncategorized/124-revision-v1/.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
